---
import ButtonTo from './ButtonTo.astro';
---

<section class='w-full h-full bg-fixed' id='services'>
  <div
    class='w-full h-full bg-gray-950 bg-opacity-70 py-32 px-10 lg:px-0 text-white flex flex-col justify-center items-center'
  >
    <h3 class='font-semibold text-4xl lg:text-7xl lg:w-3/4 text-center'>
      It's time to boost your online presence
    </h3>
    <p class='lg:w-3/5 my-10 text-lg'>
      With the new technologies coming out every day, it is undeniable that this
      is the optimal time to consider the importance of digitizing your
      business. Whether you are looking to promote your company, improve
      interaction with your clients or simply expand your brand, we are here to
      give you support.
    </p>

    <div class='flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-4'>
      <ButtonTo to='/services' text='Learn about our services' />
      <a
        href='/contact'
        class='px-6 py-2 bg-white text-center text-black rounded-full hover:border-2 hover:bg-gray-400 outline-none cursor-pointer border-black transition-all ease-in-out'
        >Request information</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style scoped>
  #services {
    background-image: url('../assets/services.jpg');
    background-position: center;
    background-size: cover;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
  }
</style>
